246
00:11:44,706 --> 00:11:45,873
Look, i'm going
to go to main street

247
00:11:45,941 --> 00:11:47,675
And i'm going to go west
and south, all right?

248
00:11:47,743 --> 00:11:48,709
You guys go south
and east, please.

249
00:11:48,777 --> 00:11:50,878
I'm just gonna stay here,

250
00:11:50,946 --> 00:11:52,446
In case the police come
or anybody calls.

251
00:11:52,514 --> 00:11:53,948
I'll be here.
do you have your cell phone?

252
00:11:54,015 --> 00:11:55,883
Yeah, in my purse.

253
00:11:55,951 --> 00:11:57,918
Where are my car keys?

254
00:11:57,986 --> 00:11:59,253
Mel...
not now.

